      <title>债券交易员对日本央行发出的任何购买信号感到紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/bond-traders-on-tenterhooks-for-any-signal-from-boj-on-purchases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员在日本央行本周召开的会议上感到紧张，因为他们担心日本央行购买主权债务的政策是否有任何改变的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/bond-traders-on-tenterhooks-for-any-signal-from-boj-on-purchases</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 20:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行维勒鲁瓦称石油不确定性不会阻止六月降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/ecb-s-villeroy-says-oil-uncertainty-won-t-stop-june-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加豪 (Francois Villeroy de Galhau) 表示，欧洲央行不会因油价不确定性而放弃 6 月份的首次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/ecb-s-villeroy-says-oil-uncertainty-won-t-stop-june-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 19:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易商期待拍卖创纪录，标志着 5% 收益率已达峰值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/bond-traders-look-to-record-auction-for-sign-5-yield-is-peak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国国债有望迎来今年最糟糕的一个月，大量拍卖即将到来，这是对收益率在达到 2024 年最高水平后是否已见顶的重大考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/bond-traders-look-to-record-auction-for-sign-5-yield-is-peak</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利对中国钢铁征收关税以支持当地工业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/chile-slaps-tariffs-on-chinese-steel-to-bolster-local-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利对该国采矿业使用的中国钢铁产品征收临时反倾销关税，以支持摇摇欲坠的当地钢厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/chile-slaps-tariffs-on-chinese-steel-to-bolster-local-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 18:11:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨对德国经济持乐观态度，理由是通胀和就业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/scholz-optimistic-on-german-economy-citing-inflation-and-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨对德国的经济前景持乐观态度，他表示，由于能源成本下降，就业率创历史新高，通胀放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/scholz-optimistic-on-german-economy-citing-inflation-and-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 17:56:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
